{"tid":1988524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方答問沒回應831事件死傷人數  江永祥：只有懼怕警方正義的人, 才想處長辭職","createTime":"2020-04-25T09:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T09:29:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"37a8f264ec97d98a01eee6c69fdb6da1357f79cc","tid":1988524,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:15:16.000Z","msg":"警方早前在社交網站上就答問大會收集提問, 今日揀選 50 條問題拍片回應, 包括元朗721、太子站831事件.<br />\n<br />\n        短片約長6分鐘, 40多條回應投考警察的要求、 不同部門的工作、 警隊裝備、公共關係科等問題, 被問到外界對警隊有誤解, 有甚麽想法, 代表就指吃力不討好, 但會繼續努力消除市民對警隊的誤解.<br />\n<br />\n        公共關係科高級警司江永祥回應4條具爭議性問題. 他指警方一直調查721事件, 至今拘捕37人, 當中7人已提堂. 他沒有直接回應831事件死傷人數, 只是說「死嘅係自己嘅腦細胞」.<br />\n<br />\n        對於七警案終審涉案5警罪名成立, 他指警方會根據公務員守則和警隊條例跟進.<br />\n<br />\n        他回應警務處處長鄧炳強幾時下台的提問時說, 只有懼怕警方正義的人, 才想處長辭職.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20200425161520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20200425161520&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=4bd3690b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20200425161520</a>"},{"pid":"ae8242e42a9fe4405439e4e8736d3989667bc045","tid":1988524,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:15:50.000Z","msg":"(重開)香港社會運動需要轉型<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1988467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1988467</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixjbr30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fixjbr30.jpg&h=3dd23a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuJC633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuJC633.jpg&h=bd20a436&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"855d2c53b018183ef99f0c5942c2f43027ec515c","tid":1988524,"uid":215763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"處長同散仔都係狗，不用分得